,Recommended,285310,32424064,Posted: 14 June,all,spaceduck,"If you are having Trouble playing after installing, ex: pressing play and nothing happens. Try this! - Go to the Control Panel and click Programs and Features. On the left side is ""Turn Windows Features on or off"". A small box will appear, scroll down to ""Legacy Components"". Check everything under Legacy Components. Make sure its an actual checkmark and not a small dot in the box."
