76561197996660728,Recommended,285310,10985268,"Posted: 30 June, 2014",all,serrao.matt,"[Solved] Windows 7 64-Bit black screen w/ music problem: Initially, the program would load and would display only a low res/ color bit screen with the classic rollercoaster startup music in the background. The problem was isolated to a driver issue with the radeon 7760m graphics card. To solve, switched to intel hd 3000 graphics and ran program as admin with vista sp2 compat mode. No other issues since, great game!"
